WEBVTT

00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:02.440
Good morning to all who are interested

00:00:02.450 --> 00:00:03.680
in our course.

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:05.120
My name is Dmitry Barsukov.

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:08.740
I am a coach and business consultant

00:00:08.750 --> 00:00:09.680
and I am dealing with

00:00:09.690 --> 00:00:11.480
organizational development

00:00:11.490 --> 00:00:13.200
issues and some legal aspects of

00:00:13.210 --> 00:00:14.600
entrepreneurial activities.

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:16.700
Our course is called “Legal

00:00:16.710 --> 00:00:18.020
Foundations of Entrepreneurship”

00:00:18.030 --> 00:00:21.300
and focuses on the main key

00:00:21.310 --> 00:00:25.120
points of creating enterprises.

00:00:25.380 --> 00:00:28.420
It does not claim to be a depth

00:00:28.430 --> 00:00:33.140
or width of coverage and is

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:35.380
intended, first of all,

00:00:35.390 --> 00:00:37.340
to help entrepreneurs to navigate

00:00:37.350 --> 00:00:39.440
in the jungles of Russian

00:00:39.450 --> 00:00:41.600
laws governing business activities.

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:44.440
Therefore, preparing it, I tried

00:00:44.450 --> 00:00:47.280
to look at entrepreneurial activities,

00:00:47.290 --> 00:00:49.600
the legal issues of entrepreneurial

00:00:49.610 --> 00:00:51.560
activities through the eyes

00:00:51.570 --> 00:00:55.920
of a simple citizen who

00:00:55.930 --> 00:00:58.460
decided to start his business.

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:01.320
So what is entrepreneurship?

00:01:01.940 --> 00:01:04.320
The Civil Code gives a clear

00:01:04.330 --> 00:01:05.780
and simple definition

00:01:05.790 --> 00:01:07.460
of business activity.

00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:08.920
Entrepreneurial activity is independent,

00:01:08.930 --> 00:01:10.660
carried out at your own

00:01:10.670 --> 00:01:12.680
risk and risk, aimed at systematic

00:01:12.690 --> 00:01:14.260
earning profits from

00:01:14.270 --> 00:01:16.580
the use of property, the sale

00:01:16.590 --> 00:01:19.000
of goods, the performance of works,

00:01:19.010 --> 00:01:20.980
the provision of services

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:22.640
by persons registered

00:01:22.650 --> 00:01:24.420
in this capacity in

00:01:24.430 --> 00:01:26.780
the established legal order.

00:01:29.140 --> 00:01:30.840
What laws govern

00:01:30.850 --> 00:01:32.160
business?

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:34.780
Let us list them briefly.

00:01:34.900 --> 00:01:36.420
This is the Civil Code, first

00:01:36.430 --> 00:01:40.240
of all, the Tax Code, the Law on

00:01:40.250 --> 00:01:41.440
the Limited Liability Company,

00:01:41.450 --> 00:01:44.020
the Law on Both Joint Stock

00:01:44.030 --> 00:01:46.440
Companies, the Law on Non-

00:01:46.450 --> 00:01:48.720
Profit Organizations, the Law

00:01:48.730 --> 00:01:50.940
on Licensing, the Customs

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:54.920
Code and some other laws that

00:01:54.930 --> 00:01:55.920
are usually used less often

00:01:55.930 --> 00:01:59.700
in business activities.

00:01:59.820 --> 00:02:02.160
Participants in the relations

00:02:02.170 --> 00:02:05.460
regulated by the Civil

00:02:05.470 --> 00:02:06.980
Code legislation are

00:02:06.990 --> 00:02:10.920
citizens and legal entities.

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:15.500
The rules established

00:02:15.510 --> 00:02:18.960
for legal entities in

00:02:18.970 --> 00:02:20.440
the part concerning business

00:02:20.450 --> 00:02:21.640
activities also

00:02:21.650 --> 00:02:24.440
apply to natural persons.

00:02:24.820 --> 00:02:26.120
Even if you

00:02:26.130 --> 00:02:28.120
are not registered

00:02:28.130 --> 00:02:30.180
as an entrepreneur,

00:02:30.190 --> 00:02:32.580
but do this, you

00:02:32.590 --> 00:02:34.020
are subject

00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:36.760
to all relevant laws.

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:39.200
Citizens have the right to

00:02:39.210 --> 00:02:40.600
engage in entrepreneurial activities

00:02:40.610 --> 00:02:42.300
without forming a legal entity

00:02:42.310 --> 00:02:43.460
from the moment of state

00:02:43.470 --> 00:02:44.820
registration as an

00:02:44.830 --> 00:02:46.240
individual entrepreneur.

00:02:48.540 --> 00:02:51.800
In addition, there are such forms

00:02:51.810 --> 00:02:53.400
of entrepreneurial activity that

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:56.340
are issued in the form of registration

00:02:56.350 --> 00:02:59.360
of a legal entity, this is LLC,

00:02:59.370 --> 00:03:01.720
LLC and so on.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:04.100
And engaging in business activities,

00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:06.220
that is, these organizations

00:03:06.230 --> 00:03:08.980
can start working from the

00:03:08.990 --> 00:03:11.080
moment of state registration.

00:03:12.940 --> 00:03:14.940
Let us consider the types

00:03:14.950 --> 00:03:16.320
of organizational and legal forms

00:03:16.540 --> 00:03:19.900
that are convenient for the implementation

00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:21.420
of business activities.

00:03:22.420 --> 00:03:23.700
This is, as we have said,

00:03:23.710 --> 00:03:25.580
an individual entrepreneur.

00:03:26.500 --> 00:03:27.980
The second form, the

00:03:27.990 --> 00:03:30.820
most common and the simplest

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:31.780
after the individual

00:03:31.790 --> 00:03:33.240
entrepreneur, is a society

00:03:33.320 --> 00:03:34.860
bounded by responsibility.

00:03:35.860 --> 00:03:37.780
There are also closed joint-stock

00:03:37.790 --> 00:03:40.120
companies and various non-

00:03:40.130 --> 00:03:42.320
profit organizations.

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:47.080
What are the advantages

00:03:47.090 --> 00:03:48.760
of an individual entrepreneur?

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:52.180
First of all, it is easy to register.

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:55.380
The minimum state duty is 400 rubles,

00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:58.180
some notarial expenses, the period

00:03:58.380 --> 00:04:00.740
of registration is 5 working days,

00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:04.340
the minimum set of documents,

00:04:04.820 --> 00:04:08.160
certificates of registration

00:04:08.170 --> 00:04:12.000
and certificates of the right to apply

00:04:12.010 --> 00:04:16.280
one or another type of taxation

00:04:16.290 --> 00:04:18.460
if necessary.

00:04:19.060 --> 00:04:20.680
In the certificate of registration

00:04:20.690 --> 00:04:23.120
is recorded only the name

00:04:23.130 --> 00:04:24.420
of the entrepreneur.

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:29.020
No names are allowed.

00:04:31.100 --> 00:04:32.960
Previously, this was possible,

00:04:32.970 --> 00:04:34.680
but today as the name of

00:04:34.690 --> 00:04:37.400
your company will only appear

00:04:37.410 --> 00:04:40.200
the name of their fatherland.

00:04:40.460 --> 00:04:43.380
The printing only shows

00:04:43.390 --> 00:04:44.400
their name.

00:04:44.760 --> 00:04:46.040
The legal address

00:04:46.050 --> 00:04:48.140
of the entrepreneur is his

00:04:48.150 --> 00:04:49.780
home address.

00:04:49.820 --> 00:04:52.280
What other points should be

00:04:52.290 --> 00:04:56.700
noted in relation to the convenience

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:59.360
of using such an organizational

00:04:59.370 --> 00:05:01.980
and legal form as an individual entrepreneur?

00:05:04.640 --> 00:05:07.440
First of all, this is convenient not

00:05:07.450 --> 00:05:09.360
only in the registration, but also

00:05:09.370 --> 00:05:13.280
in the liquidation of an individual entrepreneur.

00:05:13.960 --> 00:05:16.080
In Russia, as in the rest of the

00:05:16.700 --> 00:05:19.020
world, it is much easier to register

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:22.340
a company than to liquidate it.

00:05:23.580 --> 00:05:24.960
In the case of an individual

00:05:24.970 --> 00:05:28.800
entrepreneur, this procedure is

00:05:28.810 --> 00:05:32.160
easier than in the case

00:05:32.170 --> 00:05:34.020
of legal entities.

00:05:35.740 --> 00:05:38.380
If the entrepreneur decides that he

00:05:38.390 --> 00:05:40.800
no longer wants to engage in his activity

00:05:40.810 --> 00:05:43.600
and wants to close his business, then

00:05:43.610 --> 00:05:46.540
he, first of all, needs to pay all

00:05:47.100 --> 00:05:50.200
taxes, write to the tax inspectorate

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.760
the appropriate statement and

00:05:52.770 --> 00:05:55.060
file it, or about the suspension

00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:57.040
of activities, which

00:05:57.050 --> 00:05:58.920
is also possible, or about

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:00.500
liquidation.

00:06:00.510 --> 00:06:04.280
If the tax inspectors have no claims

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:07.400
to you on payment of taxes and there

00:06:07.410 --> 00:06:10.780
is no reason to check you

00:06:10.790 --> 00:06:14.540
seriously, then this procedure

00:06:14.550 --> 00:06:16.280
for suspension of activity

00:06:16.290 --> 00:06:21.040
or liquidation is actually completed.

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:24.260
In the event of liquidation, you

00:06:24.270 --> 00:06:26.020
will be issued a certificate.

00:06:26.700 --> 00:06:27.720
An individual entrepreneur

00:06:29.510 --> 00:06:32.740
can use several forms of taxation

00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:34.720
and reporting.

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:37.500
This is standard taxation, a simplified

00:06:37.740 --> 00:06:40.900
system, a patent and a single

00:06:40.910 --> 00:06:43.020
tax on the intended income.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.700
What taxes do entrepreneurs

00:06:45.710 --> 00:06:48.240
pay in the case of standard taxation?

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:51.740
This is 13% of the amount

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:53.120
of income, reduced

00:06:53.130 --> 00:06:56.240
by the amounts of the deductions,

00:06:56.250 --> 00:07:00.220
value added tax, 10% or 18%.

00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:04.600
10% is the VAT rate that is

00:07:04.610 --> 00:07:06.880
usually applied to foodstuffs

00:07:06.890 --> 00:07:08.760
and some other groups

00:07:08.770 --> 00:07:10.900
of goods.

00:07:11.300 --> 00:07:14.220
This is described in Article 145

00:07:14.230 --> 00:07:15.380
of the Tax Code.

00:07:16.260 --> 00:07:19.840
The single social tax on the income

00:07:19.850 --> 00:07:23.440
of the entrepreneur minus the income

00:07:23.450 --> 00:07:28.120
of 100 and below according

00:07:28.130 --> 00:07:31.360
to the scale provided by the tax code.

00:07:31.370 --> 00:07:35.220
And 26% of the single social tax from

00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:37.480
the salary fund, if the

00:07:37.490 --> 00:07:40.420
entrepreneur employs employees.

00:07:40.900 --> 00:07:43.960
These are also some other taxes due

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:45.560
to the specifics of the

00:07:45.570 --> 00:07:48.900
activity of a particular entrepreneur.

00:07:48.910 --> 00:07:52.020
Customs payments, excise duties,

00:07:52.030 --> 00:07:54.040
mineral tax, if you suddenly

00:07:54.100 --> 00:07:56.220
decide to mine such,

00:07:56.230 --> 00:08:01.160
and some other taxes.

00:08:01.500 --> 00:08:03.420
But, as a rule, individual entrepreneurs

00:08:03.430 --> 00:08:05.580
rarely carry out such a

00:08:05.590 --> 00:08:07.960
complex activity.

00:08:08.360 --> 00:08:09.520
Individual entrepreneurs keep

00:08:09.530 --> 00:08:11.820
records of income and expenses

00:08:11.830 --> 00:08:14.140
in the manner established by the

00:08:14.150 --> 00:08:17.200
tax legislation and the law

00:08:17.210 --> 00:08:19.300
on accounting.

00:08:19.440 --> 00:08:21.440
The procedure for accounting of income and

00:08:21.450 --> 00:08:23.400
expenses and economic operations

00:08:23.410 --> 00:08:25.300
for individual entrepreneurs is provided

00:08:25.310 --> 00:08:30.400
by the order of the Ministry of Finance,

00:08:30.410 --> 00:08:34.740
and taxes are accounted for by the accounting

00:08:34.750 --> 00:08:36.820
book of income and expenses

00:08:36.830 --> 00:08:38.180
of economic operations

00:08:38.190 --> 00:08:39.420
of the individual entrepreneur.

00:08:40.020 --> 00:08:42.080
This procedure does not apply

00:08:42.090 --> 00:08:44.300
to the income of an individual

00:08:44.310 --> 00:08:45.880
entrepreneur if he

00:08:45.890 --> 00:08:49.620
uses a simplified tax system.

00:08:49.940 --> 00:08:50.920
Today, entrepreneurs

00:08:50.930 --> 00:08:53.260
rarely use such a

00:08:53.270 --> 00:08:55.920
standard tax system.

00:08:56.400 --> 00:08:58.800
A much more common

00:08:58.810 --> 00:09:01.240
taxation and patents system.

00:09:01.250 --> 00:09:02.580


00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:06.260
What is a simplified tax system?

00:09:07.900 --> 00:09:14.040
It includes two types of taxation.

00:09:14.050 --> 00:09:18.740
The first is 6% of the income that

00:09:18.750 --> 00:09:21.760
the entrepreneur receives in the form

00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:24.100
of gross income.

00:09:24.440 --> 00:09:26.020
Such a system of taxation is

00:09:26.030 --> 00:09:28.120
convenient for those entrepreneurs

00:09:28.440 --> 00:09:31.880
who carry out activities that

00:09:31.890 --> 00:09:35.080
do not involve large

00:09:35.460 --> 00:09:37.620
significant costs.

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:42.980
These are services, as a

00:09:42.990 --> 00:09:44.660
rule, and some other activities.

00:09:44.900 --> 00:09:47.220
The second form of taxation in the

00:09:47.230 --> 00:09:50.380
simplified system is 15% of the difference

00:09:50.390 --> 00:09:53.480
between income and expenses.

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:56.700
This form of taxation is convenient

00:09:56.710 --> 00:09:59.120
in trade and production, where

00:09:59.130 --> 00:10:03.680
costs are large and constant.

00:10:03.690 --> 00:10:06.380
It is necessary to keep in mind that

00:10:06.390 --> 00:10:09.400
the expenditure articles, clearly regulated

00:10:09.410 --> 00:10:11.560
by the tax code and the tax inspection,

00:10:11.570 --> 00:10:13.720
are treated to them quite

00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:15.580
strictly.

00:10:15.900 --> 00:10:18.600
Therefore, when you introduce

00:10:18.610 --> 00:10:21.020
your activity, you need to clearly

00:10:21.030 --> 00:10:23.780
document all your expenses

00:10:23.790 --> 00:10:26.080
so that you do not have any

00:10:26.090 --> 00:10:29.560
disagreements with the tax inspectorate.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:32.520
If you hire employees, you must

00:10:32.530 --> 00:10:34.360
pay 10% in pensions, savings

00:10:34.370 --> 00:10:35.720
and insurance contributions

00:10:35.730 --> 00:10:38.740
from the salary fund and

00:10:38.750 --> 00:10:45.060
0.2% from the salary fund for

00:10:45.070 --> 00:10:46.440
injury.

00:10:46.660 --> 00:10:47.760
If an individual entrepreneur

00:10:47.770 --> 00:10:49.200
does not have any employees,

00:10:49.210 --> 00:10:54.000
the persons born in 1966 and

00:10:54.010 --> 00:10:56.460
older are obliged to pay a fixed 100

00:10:56.470 --> 00:10:58.560
rubles for the insurance

00:10:58.570 --> 00:11:00.100
part of the pension.

00:11:02.820 --> 00:11:06.220
Persons born in 1967 and younger are

00:11:06.230 --> 00:11:08.420
obliged to pay the same 100 rubles

00:11:08.430 --> 00:11:10.660
and 50 rubles on the cumulative

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:12.840
part of the pension.

00:11:13.340 --> 00:11:14.660
In addition, an individual entrepreneur

00:11:14.670 --> 00:11:16.160
under a contract with a pension

00:11:16.170 --> 00:11:18.160
fund can voluntarily

00:11:18.170 --> 00:11:21.880
increase these amounts of deductions.

00:11:22.300 --> 00:11:23.360
In order to use the simplified

00:11:23.370 --> 00:11:24.740
tax system, you must

00:11:24.750 --> 00:11:27.840
submit the relevant

00:11:27.850 --> 00:11:29.920
application when registering

00:11:29.930 --> 00:11:32.040
you as an individual

00:11:32.050 --> 00:11:33.420
entrepreneur.

00:11:34.780 --> 00:11:38.180
If you have already carried out some

00:11:38.190 --> 00:11:40.540
activity and decided to move to the

00:11:40.550 --> 00:11:42.900
simplified system, then you are

00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:45.280
obliged to file a application

00:11:45.290 --> 00:11:48.300
to the tax inspectorate from October

00:11:48.310 --> 00:11:53.800
1 to November 30 of the previous year,

00:11:53.810 --> 00:11:56.520
in which you want to carry out

00:11:56.530 --> 00:11:59.100
your activities under the simplified

00:11:59.110 --> 00:12:00.640
taxation system.

00:12:01.460 --> 00:12:03.560
Income of the taxpayer,

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:05.240
switching to the simplified

00:12:05.250 --> 00:12:08.720
system, should not exceed

00:12:08.730 --> 00:12:11.100
15 million rubles, multiplied

00:12:11.110 --> 00:12:13.800
by the corresponding

00:12:13.810 --> 00:12:15.240
coefficients, which

00:12:15.250 --> 00:12:16.460
are established

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:18.320
by the government.

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:20.860
The simplified system of taxation

00:12:20.870 --> 00:12:23.000
of organizations, the

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:25.360
residual value of funds and non-

00:12:25.370 --> 00:12:27.240
material assets exceeds

00:12:27.250 --> 00:12:29.540
100 million rubles, as well as

00:12:29.550 --> 00:12:31.860
taxpayers listed in Article

00:12:31.870 --> 00:12:34.200
246 of the Tax Code of the Russian

00:12:34.210 --> 00:12:38.420
Federation, shall not

00:12:38.430 --> 00:12:39.600
be applied.

00:12:39.940 --> 00:12:42.820
In the current year, the income

00:12:42.830 --> 00:12:44.640
of the taxpayer should not

00:12:44.650 --> 00:12:46.640
exceed 20 million rubles.

00:12:47.300 --> 00:12:49.580
In the event of exceeding this amount

00:12:49.590 --> 00:12:52.220
or if the residual value of the assets

00:12:52.230 --> 00:12:54.060
and non-material assets exceeds 100

00:12:54.070 --> 00:12:57.120
million rubles and the average

00:12:57.130 --> 00:12:58.580
number of employees exceeds 100

00:12:58.590 --> 00:13:00.400
persons, the taxpayer

00:13:00.860 --> 00:13:02.060
is considered to have moved

00:13:02.070 --> 00:13:03.820
to the general tax regime

00:13:03.830 --> 00:13:05.960
from the beginning of the

00:13:05.970 --> 00:13:07.820
quarter in which this excess

00:13:07.830 --> 00:13:08.880
was allowed.

00:13:09.220 --> 00:13:13.440
Another form of taxation of

00:13:13.450 --> 00:13:14.880
individual entrepreneurs

00:13:14.890 --> 00:13:17.120
is patent.

00:13:17.400 --> 00:13:20.980
It is used widely and can

00:13:20.990 --> 00:13:23.280
only be used by individual

00:13:23.290 --> 00:13:25.160
entrepreneurs.

00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:27.600
If the simplified system can be

00:13:27.610 --> 00:13:29.900
applied by individual entrepreneurs

00:13:29.910 --> 00:13:31.760
and other legal entities,

00:13:31.770 --> 00:13:34.500
then the patent is only applied

00:13:34.510 --> 00:13:35.900
by individual entrepreneurs.

00:13:36.580 --> 00:13:38.220
A patent is a fixed tax determined

00:13:38.230 --> 00:13:40.080
by federal laws and laws of the

00:13:40.090 --> 00:13:41.980
constituent entities of the Russian

00:13:41.990 --> 00:13:43.900
Federation on certain

00:13:43.910 --> 00:13:45.760
types of activities of an

00:13:45.770 --> 00:13:47.980
individual entrepreneur.

00:13:48.260 --> 00:13:49.920
The cost of a patent is calculated by the

00:13:49.930 --> 00:13:51.680
tax authorities according to

00:13:51.690 --> 00:13:53.800
the scale established by the laws.

00:13:53.960 --> 00:13:54.980
In the case of the application

00:13:54.990 --> 00:13:56.560
of the simplified taxation system

00:13:56.570 --> 00:13:59.680
by entrepreneurs based on a patent,

00:13:59.690 --> 00:14:02.620
they are subject to the norms established

00:14:02.630 --> 00:14:06.020
by citizens with the Tax

00:14:06.030 --> 00:14:09.580
Code of the Russian Federation.

00:14:09.590 --> 00:14:11.600
The individual entrepreneur

00:14:11.610 --> 00:14:14.880
should not attract employees.

