This is quite a ridiculous situation,

00:47:12.880 --> 00:47:16.250
because you can change your

00:47:16.260 --> 00:47:20.850
office several times a year.

00:47:20.930 --> 00:47:22.490
Maybe this happens.

00:47:22.690 --> 00:47:25.990
And every time you ideally should

00:47:26.000 --> 00:47:27.690
run to the tax inspectorate and

00:47:27.700 --> 00:47:29.730
make changes to the charter documents.

00:47:29.930 --> 00:47:33.250
In practice, most organizations

00:47:33.260 --> 00:47:36.630
have a formal legal address,

00:47:36.640 --> 00:47:39.330
supported by some formal

00:47:39.340 --> 00:47:41.650
contract concluded with

00:47:41.660 --> 00:47:44.630
some organization, with

00:47:44.640 --> 00:47:49.350
the owner of some premises.

00:47:49.730 --> 00:47:52.890
Having such a legal address, they move

00:47:52.900 --> 00:47:55.890
from one office to another and

00:47:55.900 --> 00:47:59.770
do not submit information about this

00:47:59.780 --> 00:48:01.130
to the tax inspectorate.

00:48:01.450 --> 00:48:05.510
And tax inspections look through their

00:48:05.520 --> 00:48:08.230
fingers at this, then in order to

00:48:08.240 --> 00:48:11.370
increase the collection of taxes or

00:48:11.380 --> 00:48:14.230
when some new directions and trends

00:48:14.490 --> 00:48:18.150
appear, they periodically

00:48:18.160 --> 00:48:20.370
start to shake entrepreneurs

00:48:20.380 --> 00:48:23.950
again in connection with this

00:48:23.960 --> 00:48:25.610
legal address and demand that

00:48:25.620 --> 00:48:30.410
the location of the organization

00:48:30.420 --> 00:48:35.910
corresponds to its actual address.

00:48:35.950 --> 00:48:39.270
The address at which he is currently

00:48:39.280 --> 00:48:39.910
working.

00:48:40.230 --> 00:48:41.770
And then taxpayers are forced

00:48:41.780 --> 00:48:45.770
to look again for ways to get

00:48:45.780 --> 00:48:47.810
out of the situation.

00:48:48.170 --> 00:48:50.850
But you may be told that you

00:48:50.860 --> 00:48:53.030
will work for a long time and

00:48:53.040 --> 00:48:55.810
with a formal legal address.

00:48:56.350 --> 00:48:57.750
But if the tax authority

00:48:57.760 --> 00:49:01.070
wants, it will force you to change

00:49:01.080 --> 00:49:04.090
it by blocking the account and

00:49:04.100 --> 00:49:07.090
applying other preventive administrative

00:49:07.100 --> 00:49:08.870
measures.

00:49:10.570 --> 00:49:13.990
Let us now consider another type

00:49:14.000 --> 00:49:17.250
of organizations, which are

00:49:17.260 --> 00:49:20.450
also widely used by entrepreneurs,

00:49:20.460 --> 00:49:22.270
although they are called

00:49:22.280 --> 00:49:25.190
non-profit organizations.

00:49:25.250 --> 00:49:26.470
A non-profit organization

00:49:26.480 --> 00:49:28.670
is an organization that does not

00:49:28.680 --> 00:49:31.370
have profit as its main purpose

00:49:31.380 --> 00:49:35.110
of activity and does not distribute

00:49:35.120 --> 00:49:38.430
profit among its members.

00:49:38.530 --> 00:49:40.930
This wording is taken directly

00:49:40.940 --> 00:49:42.450
from the law.

00:49:42.550 --> 00:49:46.110
The law believes that non-

00:49:46.120 --> 00:49:48.930
profit organizations can be

00:49:48.940 --> 00:49:51.270
created to some social, charitable

00:49:51.390 --> 00:49:54.990
goals and the like.

00:49:55.190 --> 00:49:59.370
Although in practice, for example,

00:49:59.380 --> 00:50:03.470
all educational institutions, even commercial,

00:50:03.480 --> 00:50:05.910
in Russia are registered

00:50:05.920 --> 00:50:07.250
as non-profit organizations,

00:50:07.260 --> 00:50:09.590
but the owners created them

00:50:09.600 --> 00:50:13.770
precisely for the purpose of

00:50:13.780 --> 00:50:15.330
earning profit.

00:50:15.710 --> 00:50:16.830
In general, educational

00:50:16.840 --> 00:50:18.750
activities are quite

00:50:18.760 --> 00:50:21.350
profitable and quite

00:50:21.360 --> 00:50:22.750
commercial.

00:50:23.050 --> 00:50:26.670
But why is it that our state and our

00:50:26.680 --> 00:50:30.570
licensing bodies have an approach

00:50:30.580 --> 00:50:33.270
to educational organizations

00:50:33.280 --> 00:50:36.490
that they require that an organization

00:50:36.500 --> 00:50:39.730
that wants to provide educational

00:50:39.910 --> 00:50:41.390
services has such

00:50:41.400 --> 00:50:44.650
an organizational and

00:50:44.660 --> 00:50:47.190
legal form in the form

00:50:47.200 --> 00:50:50.950
of a non-profit organization.

00:50:51.110 --> 00:50:53.070
We will only talk about those non-

00:50:53.080 --> 00:50:55.310
profit organizations, organizations

00:50:55.530 --> 00:50:58.110
that do not belong to the category

00:50:58.120 --> 00:51:00.790
of public organizations.

00:51:01.090 --> 00:51:03.430
As a matter of fact, social movements,

00:51:03.870 --> 00:51:07.530
social foundations, political movements,

00:51:07.540 --> 00:51:10.930
religious movements and the like.

00:51:11.170 --> 00:51:12.790
The organizations we will consider

00:51:12.800 --> 00:51:14.670
are simple non-profit funds,

00:51:14.680 --> 00:51:17.030
autonomous non-profit organizations,

00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:18.770
institutions and

00:51:18.990 --> 00:51:21.070
partnerships.

00:51:21.310 --> 00:51:22.850
The law on non-profit organizations

00:51:22.860 --> 00:51:24.970
states that a non-profit

00:51:24.980 --> 00:51:26.990
organization can only carry

00:51:27.000 --> 00:51:28.550
out business activities insofar

00:51:28.560 --> 00:51:30.170
as it serves you can engage

00:51:33.450 --> 00:51:39.530
in some commercial activity

00:51:39.540 --> 00:51:43.270
in order to direct the profits

00:51:43.280 --> 00:51:46.190
received to the purposes

00:51:46.200 --> 00:51:49.170
for which the organization

00:51:49.180 --> 00:51:52.010
was created.

00:51:52.130 --> 00:51:55.350
That is, say, for the purpose of developing

00:51:55.360 --> 00:51:59.690
education or for the purpose of conducting

00:51:59.700 --> 00:52:04.910
a gas pipeline to the country parks,

00:52:04.920 --> 00:52:07.810
in some country partnership.

00:52:08.130 --> 00:52:09.810
This can be any activity

00:52:09.820 --> 00:52:13.030
that brings profit.

00:52:13.310 --> 00:52:14.770
This is the production of some

00:52:14.780 --> 00:52:19.570
goods and the provision of some services

00:52:19.580 --> 00:52:21.110
and so on and so on.

00:52:21.270 --> 00:52:23.190
In fact, any activity that is

00:52:23.430 --> 00:52:26.510
carried out by ordinary commercial

00:52:26.520 --> 00:52:28.110
organizations.

00:52:28.290 --> 00:52:30.190
Thus, if you follow the letter

00:52:30.200 --> 00:52:33.330
of the law, the organizational and

00:52:33.340 --> 00:52:34.870
legal form of non-profit organizations

00:52:34.880 --> 00:52:37.090
is not intended for doing

00:52:37.100 --> 00:52:38.850
business.

00:52:39.170 --> 00:52:41.130
But, as is known, reality differs

00:52:41.140 --> 00:52:44.790
from legislation and entrepreneurs

00:52:44.800 --> 00:52:47.310
then, when such an organizational

00:52:47.320 --> 00:52:49.210
legal form is convenient for

00:52:49.220 --> 00:52:53.430
them, they use it for their

00:52:53.440 --> 00:52:54.310
purposes.

00:52:54.370 --> 00:52:55.970
A distinctive feature of non-

00:52:55.980 --> 00:52:57.790
profit organizations is also

00:52:57.800 --> 00:53:00.070
that, in addition to the profits

00:53:00.080 --> 00:53:03.410
derived from commercial activities,

00:53:03.420 --> 00:53:06.370
the sources of the formation

00:53:06.380 --> 00:53:08.190
of property of the non-

00:53:08.200 --> 00:53:10.290
profit organization can be regular

00:53:10.300 --> 00:53:12.970
and one-off receipts from

00:53:12.980 --> 00:53:16.290
founders and voluntary

00:53:16.300 --> 00:53:18.790
property contributions and

00:53:18.800 --> 00:53:19.670
donations.

00:53:19.950 --> 00:53:22.110
These money receipts, if they are spent

00:53:22.120 --> 00:53:24.110
for the chartered purposes of

00:53:24.120 --> 00:53:26.130
the organization, do not

00:53:26.140 --> 00:53:27.330
have any taxes.

00:53:27.390 --> 00:53:29.930
In different situations, this is

00:53:30.110 --> 00:53:34.110
quite convenient and, for example,

00:53:34.120 --> 00:53:36.070
when you are actually engaged in some

00:53:36.080 --> 00:53:39.390
activity aimed at achieving some

00:53:39.400 --> 00:53:43.670
there, social benefits for some

00:53:43.680 --> 00:53:46.210
group of people who have joined,

00:53:46.220 --> 00:53:48.170
you can accept membership

00:53:48.180 --> 00:53:51.250
contributions, you can peacefully,

00:53:51.260 --> 00:53:53.710
freely accept some donations,

00:53:53.720 --> 00:53:55.890
and if you will spend them for

00:53:56.150 --> 00:53:59.650
the purposes for which the

00:53:59.890 --> 00:54:01.570
organization is created,

00:54:01.580 --> 00:54:03.730
then you will not have

00:54:03.740 --> 00:54:06.610
any tax obligations.

00:54:06.650 --> 00:54:08.490
The main thing is that it

00:54:08.500 --> 00:54:11.450
is documented, clearly, properly

00:54:11.460 --> 00:54:13.090
documented, so that the tax

00:54:13.100 --> 00:54:15.030
inspectorate has no reason

00:54:15.040 --> 00:54:16.270
to make claims to you.

00:54:16.390 --> 00:54:19.330
In other situations, the

00:54:19.340 --> 00:54:20.670
commercial activities of a

00:54:20.680 --> 00:54:22.570
non-profit organization are

00:54:22.990 --> 00:54:27.480
taxed according to the same system

00:54:27.490 --> 00:54:31.840
as the activities of any LLC,

00:54:31.850 --> 00:54:32.760
for example.

00:54:32.940 --> 00:54:35.540
The procedure for registration

00:54:35.550 --> 00:54:37.460
of a non-profit organization differs

00:54:37.470 --> 00:54:40.500
from the registration of other legal

00:54:40.510 --> 00:54:43.660
entities in that the documents for registration

00:54:43.670 --> 00:54:45.760
are filed not to the tax inspection,

00:54:45.770 --> 00:54:49.120
but to the registration

00:54:49.130 --> 00:54:51.040
service of the Ministry

00:54:51.050 --> 00:54:53.520
of Justice of the Russian Federation.

00:54:54.720 --> 00:54:57.240
Non-profit organizations are

00:54:57.250 --> 00:55:01.280
registered longer than

00:55:01.290 --> 00:55:02.540
those registered

00:55:02.550 --> 00:55:06.100
by the tax inspectorate.

00:55:06.160 --> 00:55:08.720
On average, it takes about a month from

00:55:08.730 --> 00:55:11.840
the moment of submission of the documents

00:55:11.850 --> 00:55:12.780
for registration.

00:55:12.940 --> 00:55:15.020
In terms of the formation of statutory

00:55:15.030 --> 00:55:16.700
documents, the legislation

00:55:16.710 --> 00:55:19.700
gives quite wide opportunities for

00:55:19.710 --> 00:55:22.400
the establishment of the

00:55:22.410 --> 00:55:24.380
principles of management of a non-

00:55:24.390 --> 00:55:27.980
profit organization, and this

00:55:27.990 --> 00:55:29.600
is a certain convenience.

00:55:29.610 --> 00:55:33.260
You can quite freely describe those

00:55:33.480 --> 00:55:37.530
principles that are important to

00:55:37.540 --> 00:55:41.310
you and correspond to the specifics

00:55:41.320 --> 00:55:43.130
of your activity to the maximum

00:55:43.140 --> 00:55:44.570
extent possible.

00:55:47.490 --> 00:55:48.390
The next aspect

00:55:48.400 --> 00:55:49.810
of business activity

00:55:49.830 --> 00:55:51.870
that cannot be stopped

00:55:52.110 --> 00:55:53.650
is licensing.

00:55:53.970 --> 00:55:56.050
The types of activities that

00:55:56.060 --> 00:55:57.770
are subject to licensing are

00:55:58.210 --> 00:56:00.330
determined by the law on

00:56:00.340 --> 00:56:02.890
licensing of certain types of activities.

00:56:03.130 --> 00:56:03.930
He is called so.

00:56:04.850 --> 00:56:06.990
It contains general

00:56:07.000 --> 00:56:09.730
provisions on licensing.

00:56:10.410 --> 00:56:12.870
More detailed regulations and

00:56:12.880 --> 00:56:16.050
procedures described by regulatory

00:56:16.060 --> 00:56:20.150
acts of relevant bodies and agencies.

00:56:20.250 --> 00:56:22.110
The main activities subject

00:56:22.310 --> 00:56:24.250
to licensing are listed

00:56:24.830 --> 00:56:28.290
in Article 17 of the Licensing Act.

00:56:28.450 --> 00:56:30.610
Today, the list of these activities

00:56:30.620 --> 00:56:33.090
has been significantly reduced

00:56:33.100 --> 00:56:35.590
and much fewer business

00:56:35.600 --> 00:56:39.310
types are subject to licensing

00:56:39.320 --> 00:56:42.170
than it was five years

00:56:42.180 --> 00:56:43.010
ago.

00:56:43.270 --> 00:56:46.030
For example, this is licensing

00:56:47.550 --> 00:56:49.150
pharmaceutical activities, manufacturing

00:56:49.330 --> 00:56:50.570
of medicines, licensing

00:56:50.710 --> 00:56:54.670
of banking operations, and

00:56:54.680 --> 00:56:55.410
so on.

00:56:55.690 --> 00:56:58.350
By the way, such activities

00:56:58.360 --> 00:57:00.130
as banking, exchange

00:57:00.140 --> 00:57:03.070
activities and activities

00:57:03.080 --> 00:57:04.190
in the field of

00:57:04.200 --> 00:57:06.350
alcohol production are

00:57:06.360 --> 00:57:09.830
not regulated.

00:57:09.840 --> 00:57:11.750
In general, it is regulated not in

00:57:11.760 --> 00:57:14.090
legal licensing, but by separate

00:57:14.100 --> 00:57:15.950
normative legal acts.

00:57:16.190 --> 00:57:18.110
These laws contain the basic

00:57:18.120 --> 00:57:22.250
provisions on licensing each

00:57:22.260 --> 00:57:24.730
of the listed activities.

00:57:25.150 --> 00:57:30.130
Small business is another aspect

00:57:30.140 --> 00:57:32.550
that directly affects

00:57:32.560 --> 00:57:35.310
everyone who wants to engage

00:57:35.320 --> 00:57:37.330
in entrepreneurial activities.

00:57:37.470 --> 00:57:42.270
Until recently, the status of a small

00:57:42.280 --> 00:57:45.050
enterprise gave certain advantages

00:57:45.060 --> 00:57:46.930
to entrepreneurs.

00:57:47.170 --> 00:57:50.610
But with the simplified tax system,

00:57:50.620 --> 00:57:53.070
these advantages have come

00:57:53.080 --> 00:57:53.690
to them.

00:57:53.850 --> 00:57:56.510
Previously, only organizations

00:57:56.520 --> 00:57:59.430
registered as small business

00:57:59.440 --> 00:58:03.470
entities could work

00:58:03.480 --> 00:58:07.630
on the simplified tax system.

00:58:07.810 --> 00:58:10.450
This right is granted to any

00:58:10.460 --> 00:58:11.630
organization.

00:58:11.730 --> 00:58:15.130
Therefore, among the advantages that

00:58:15.140 --> 00:58:17.190
this status gives, the

00:58:17.200 --> 00:58:19.930
preferential rate for renting municipal

00:58:19.940 --> 00:58:25.030
real estate remains the most significant

00:58:25.040 --> 00:58:28.350
to date and is determined

00:58:28.360 --> 00:58:30.810
by specific legislative

00:58:30.820 --> 00:58:33.770
and regulatory acts of federal

00:58:33.780 --> 00:58:38.370
subjects and municipal

00:58:38.380 --> 00:58:39.850
bodies.

00:58:39.910 --> 00:58:40.990
Small business entities

00:58:41.000 --> 00:58:43.990
may be commercial organizations,

00:58:44.000 --> 00:58:47.130
mainly capital, whose

00:58:47.140 --> 00:58:50.090
share of legal entities

00:58:50.210 --> 00:58:56.650
does not exceed 25 percent.

00:58:56.890 --> 00:58:59.170
If the founders or shareholders

00:58:59.180 --> 00:59:02.510
of the company are legal

00:59:02.520 --> 00:59:06.270
persons, they must own no more

00:59:06.280 --> 00:59:09.730
than 25 percent of shares

00:59:09.740 --> 00:59:15.150
or shares in the company.

00:59:15.170 --> 00:59:17.650
In addition, the average

00:59:17.660 --> 00:59:21.210
number of employees of the

00:59:21.220 --> 00:59:23.270
small business entity may

00:59:23.280 --> 00:59:26.350
not exceed certain values

00:59:26.360 --> 00:59:29.190
set by legislation.

00:59:29.430 --> 00:59:30.830
Subjects of small business

00:59:30.840 --> 00:59:34.170
are understood as individuals

00:59:34.180 --> 00:59:37.070
engaged in entrepreneurship,

00:59:37.080 --> 00:59:38.850
i.e. individual entrepreneurs,

00:59:38.860 --> 00:59:40.190
and organizations that

00:59:40.650 --> 00:59:44.110
decided to obtain such status

00:59:44.120 --> 00:59:46.170
and corresponding

00:59:46.180 --> 00:59:47.530
requirements.

